{"tid":1589864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有料怕咩攬炒？","createTime":"2019-09-23T12:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T13:03:02.000Z","uid":73915,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"df2bbe98adfa4aa5b39f7ffecb064072752b00cf","tid":1589864,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:43:36.000Z","msg":"1。有知識，唔怕攬炒，可移民（IT狗，xx師）<br />\n2。有樓，唔怕攬炒，買樓走人（咩價賣都賺）<br />\n3。冇錢，唔怕攬炒，冇野輸（塔左仲好，免費飯）<br />\n4。後生，唔怕攬炒，大把時間（洗牌有機會）<br />\n<br />\n咩人怕攬炒？<br />\n老，冇樓，冇知識，有少少錢<br />\n即係典型廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a2f51cdb18c944b8cfe8883cbb72cce40f0c9b","tid":1589864,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:44:24.000Z","msg":"攬炒 全城爆愛滋一齊死"},{"pid":"7bbcb20dadfc693394f88807f83736de99fea195","tid":1589864,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:45:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"3fe7c21c7ab3b72ecd8c0369f03437b5eb786726","tid":1589864,"uid":70973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:50:14.000Z","msg":"930三罷=頭條&quot;香港國慶前一日淪為死城&quot;<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589862</a>"},{"pid":"79cedb6441b191556b0c29c1f96cac81eeee83d4","tid":1589864,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4a2f51cdb18c944b8cfe8883cbb72cce40f0c9b","tid":1589864,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:44:24.000Z","msg":"攬炒 全城爆愛滋一齊死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12: